ade-module-for-azure-data-factory-to-fabric">PowerShell script</a> to start your migration today. For additional guidance, check out our <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/fabric/data-factory/migrate-planning-azure-data-factory">migration overview</a> and <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/fabric/data-factory/connector-parity">connector compatibility comparison</a> documentation.',Migration_SelectFolderTitle:"Select or create a new folder for your migrated items",Migration_CancelMessage:"Migration cancelled by user",Migration_CancelTitle:"Migration cancelled",Migration_Cancel:"Cancel migration",Migration_DependencyReason:"This resource is '{0}' because it depends on '{1}' with that same status.",Migration_SummaryTitle:"Migration Summary",Migration_PopupBanner:"Starting July 1, 2026, Microsoft internal users will no longer be able to create new Azure Data Factories.",Migration_PopupInfo:"Instead you will want to begin using Data Factory in Fabric which includes all of the ADF capability in a modern SaaS environment with many new features including Copilot, Email, Teams, and Copy Job.",Migration_PopupContent:"Click the Assessment button on your ADF screen to begin the migration process to Fabric. Visit our frequently asked questions page or email us for any further questions:",Migration_ExportAssessment:"Successfully exported migration assessment",Migration_ExportResults:"Successfully exported migration results",Migration_PipelineReady:"{0} is ready to migrate.",Migration_PipelineReview:"{0} can migrate, but please review these resources before continuing:",Migration_PipelineIncompatible:"{0} cannot be migrated because these resources are incompatible:",Migration_SelectTitle:"Select what you want to upgrade",Migration_TriggerFailedToConvert:"This trigger had a problem and was unable to be migrated.",Migration_TriggerHasParameters:"This trigger has parameters which are not supported